    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sail- or power-driven watercraft of various kinds, usually light and used for racing or for recreation. In early use, yachts were fast and often used for the conveyance of royal or other important persons; in modern use, recreational yachts are luxury vessels.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
